headline: International Land Alliance Launches BOXABL at Cabo Oasis
summary: Affordable Tesla-Powered BOXABL Tiny Homes Coming to Cabo Oasis Expanding Flagship Development SAN DIEGO, Sept. 15, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- International Land Alliance, Inc. (OTCQB: ILAL) (“ILAL” or the “Company”), a global real estate investment and development firm, today announced that the wildly-popular tiny home brand, BOXABL, is now available for ordering at its flagship 500-acre Cabo Oasis beachfront development in Baja California.
